      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory, with all systems functioning perfectly and a complete service history included. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
