    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are privileged to present this superlative example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in an uncompromising, showroom state, exhibiting no discernible wear to its interior surfaces or exterior finish. Meticulously curated and maintained to the highest standards of mechanical integrity, this investment-grade specimen offers an unparalleled driving experience for the discerning collector. Its provenance and physical condition are beyond reproach, representing the pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 48500.0,
