    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 high-revving inline-six and a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example is mechanically superlative: the dual-VANOS system has been fully overhauled with Beisan seals and a cryo-treated oil pump disk, and preventative rod bearing replacement has been performed using WPC-treated bearings and ARP bolts. The rear subframe/RACP has been professionally reinforced with plates, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with fresh bushings and M-Variable differential lock engagement is seamless. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth is exceptional and the interior shows zero bolster wear. A turn-key driver for the purist demanding atmospheric performance and chassis precision.",
      "price": 44900.0,
